snippet.title: AntiChamber - Tips and Tricks and Hints - Minor Spoilers, Not a room guide
snippet.description:
Playlist: http://goo.gl/vVD8O
A general guide to some of the core concepts in Antichamber. This isn't a room by room guide, but rather a series of hints and tips to help you through some of the more challenging parts, without giving anything away.
I'll be doing an annotated map at some point.
